4.3 DUIM-DCs Module

brush-fill-style

Generic function

Summary

Returns the fill style of the brush.

Library

duim-dcs

Module

duim-dcs

Signature

brush-fill-style brush => fill-style

Arguments

brush
An instance of type <brush>.

Values

fill-style
An instance of fill-style or <boolean>.

Description

Returns the fill style of brush, or #f, if brush does not have a fill style.

See also

brush-fill-rule, page 128.

Functional Developer Library Reference: DUIM - 3 Dec 1998
